<SUBJECT>65--INTENT TO SOLE SOURCE ORTHO CLINICAL GEL CARDS   
<SOLNBR>36C24718Q9707
<ARCHDATE>11142018
<CONTACT>JOSEPH LOCKE
CONTRACTING OFFICER
